<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: #003366;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .order-details {
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .order-details th, .order-details td {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #003366;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: white;
            background: #28a745;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">Thank You for Your Order!</div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Your order has been confirmed. Below are the details:</p>
            <table class="order-details">
                <tr>
                    <th>Order Confirmation No.</th>
                    <td>#2345678</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Purchased Item(s)</th>
                    <td>$100.00</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Shipping + Handling</th>
                    <td>$10.00</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Sales Tax</th>
                    <td>$5.00</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th><strong>Total</strong></th>
                    <td><strong>$115.00</strong></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <p><strong>Delivery Address:</strong><br>675 Massachusetts Avenue, 11th Floor, Cambridge, MA 02139</p>
            <p><strong>Estimated Delivery Date:</strong><br>January 1st, 2024</p>
            <a href="#" class="button">Track Your Order</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Get 25% off your next order. Use code: THANKYOU25</p>
            <p><a href="#">Email Preferences</a> | <a href="#">Unsubscribe</a> | <a href="#">View Online</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
